headline: Arista Networks (ANET): Great Growth, Questionable Valuation
summary: Arista Networks has rallied 95% this year on the back of AI success. The company has a solid profitability record and exciting growth prospects. However, that growth is tied to AI and the resulting high valuation has made the stock a tricky investment despite its strong finances. Arista Networks specializes in software-driven cloud networking solutions […]
